# CFD_solver/ contains large Docker .tar images — excluded from git entirely.
# Note: sbatch/CFD_solver/ is also covered by this rule (no leading slash = matches anywhere in tree).
# This matters because sbatch/ was historically managed as a nested git repo (sbatch/.git) pointing
# to the same remote as the parent repo (KrisshChawla6/Shape_Evolve.git). That created a dual-tracking
# problem: the 53 files in sbatch/ were tracked by both repos simultaneously, meaning commits made
# from inside sbatch/ and commits made from the parent could silently diverge until a push/pull synced
# them via the shared remote. As of March 2026 the two histories were confirmed identical (14 commits,
# same HEAD 4dee020) and sbatch/.git was removed — sbatch/ is now managed solely from the parent repo.
CFD_solver/

# Large simulation outputs / datasets (not code)
**/results/
**/save/
environments/DrivAer_Star/data/
environments/DrivAer_Star/test_case/

# Environment variable files (may contain API keys)
**/.env
venv/

# Python
__pycache__/
# Bulk run/output artifacts
SAVED_DIRS*/
run_*/
**/run_*/
**/runs/
**/checkpoints/
**/artifacts/
**/wandb/
**/mlruns/
**/tensorboard/
**/events.out.tfevents*
**/*.npy
**/*.npz
**/*.h5
**/*.pkl

# Known heavy paths on this cluster
SAVED_DIRS_reward_ld_ratio_constrained_m02_re1e7_LAM50/
archive/
logs/
environments/solver_configs/
